    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Vaulting Over It》是一款基于物理的高难度攀爬游戏——每一次失误，都是永久的。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >物理攀爬系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/7edd7d5ea3ab4c212a672c6024ef3890.poster.avif?t=1763841496\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/7edd7d5ea3ab4c212a672c6024ef3890.webm?t=1763841496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/7edd7d5ea3ab4c212a672c6024ef3890.mp4?t=1763841496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你手里的树枝，是你最忠实的伙伴，也是你最大的敌人。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >失败本身就是特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/f8f081ae167dbad5f5fc750f953120ff.poster.avif?t=1763841496\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/f8f081ae167dbad5f5fc750f953120ff.webm?t=1763841496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/f8f081ae167dbad5f5fc750f953120ff.mp4?t=1763841496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尝试就是迈向失败的第一步。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态障碍物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/23f0132b8312fd0d7aa85d87a4c67133.poster.avif?t=1763841496\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/23f0132b8312fd0d7aa85d87a4c67133.webm?t=1763841496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/23f0132b8312fd0d7aa85d87a4c67133.mp4?t=1763841496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只会让情况变得更糟。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一张地图，没有存档点</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/4206917fab097eef45c100cf07ff0d47.poster.avif?t=1763841496\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/4206917fab097eef45c100cf07ff0d47.webm?t=1763841496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/4206917fab097eef45c100cf07ff0d47.mp4?t=1763841496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >既然可以无限重来，谁还需要进度？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全物理驱动角色系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/faaf5f87b09dd036d2b0069d5a15a705.poster.avif?t=1763841496\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/faaf5f87b09dd036d2b0069d5a15a705.webm?t=1763841496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083230/extras/faaf5f87b09dd036d2b0069d5a15a705.mp4?t=1763841496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不幸的是, 它会完全照你指令行动。</p>",
